            </div>
            <div class="callout-content">
              <strong>Pro tip:</strong> List your mid-term rental on Airbnb with a 30-night minimum stay. This is perfectly legal in Markham because it's not a short-term rental. Airbnb's monthly discount feature and search filters will show your listing to guests specifically looking for longer stays. You can also list on Furnished Finder, Kijiji, and Facebook Marketplace.
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 id="neighbouring-options">Nearby Cities Where You CAN Airbnb</h2>
          <p>If you're set on running a traditional nightly Airbnb, several cities bordering Markham have more permissive rules:</p>

          <div class="comparison-table">
            <div class="comparison-header">
              <div class="comparison-col">City</div>
              <div class="comparison-col highlight">STR Status</div>
            </div>
            <div class="comparison-row">
